{"word":"Ham","slug":"ham","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ham</b> <a href=\"#/H1990\">H1990</a><br/><a href=\"#/H2526\">H2526</a> <br/> 1. Son of Noah<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=5&verse=32'>Gen 5:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=18'>Gen 9:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=24'>Gen 9:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=4'>1Ch 1:4</a> <br/> - Provokes his father's wrath and is cursed by him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=27'>Gen 9:27</a> <br/> - His children<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=20'>Gen 10:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=16'>1Ch 1:16</a> <br/> 2. Patronymic of the descendants of Ham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=40'>1Ch 4:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=51'>Psa 78:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=23'>Psa 105:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=27'>Psa 105:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=22'>Psa 106:22</a><br/> 3. Place where Chedorlaomer smote the Zuzims<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=5'>Gen 14:5</a>"}]}